name.html: doTERRA 2019 Global Convention

description.text:
doTERRA 2019 Global Convention
We've reached max capacity, and convention is officially sold out! Email convention@doterra.com to be added to the waiting list should a ticket become available. We are beyond excited to gather together as a doTERRA community this fall!
Join us at doTERRA's Annual Global Convention September 10th-13th, 2019 in Salt Lake City to learn and celebrate! Find out more about essential oils, be inspired, and discover how you can impact lives for good. We look forward to seeing you there!
New this year, registration will open early on Monday evening. The Recognition Gala will take place on Tuesday night, and the General Sessions will take place on Wednesday, Thursday, and Friday. Empowered Success will wrap up the week on Saturday morning. 

Ticket Transfers and Cancellations 


Ticket transfer: Free (April 1–August 20, 2019). Ticket can only be transferred once. Payment is arranged by ticket holders and not facilitated by doTERRA. 


Ticket cancellation: Free (April 1–August 20, 2019)



Ticket Transfer Policy:
We can only transfer your entire order, meaning your general session ticket and all activity tickets (such as Gala, Empowered Success, Campus Tours, and Yoga) will be transferred. 
To transfer individual activity tickets, simply hand them to whomever at the event. Payment is arranged by those involved.
Fee: Free April 1–August 20. A ticket can only be transferred once.
To process your ticket transfer, email convention@doterra.com or call Member Services with your request.
Payment for transfers is arranged by you entirely. We do not transfer the payment to the new ticket holder.

Cancellation Policy:
Fee: Free April 1–August 20. 
To process your cancellation, email convention@doterra.com or call Member Services with your cancellation request. 

Track Changes Policy:
Track changes are possible based on availability. We cannot make any exceptions if tracks are already full. Email convention@doterra.com or call Member Services for track change requests.

Registration Questions 
For convention related requests, email convention@doterra.com or contact Member Services via the Live Chat link on http://doterra.com or at 1-800-411-8151. 

Please Note: 
*You must purchase a Full Conference Pass, in order to purchase any Activity Tickets. If you do not purchase a Full Conference Pass, your Activity Ticket(s) will be cancelled and refunded.
*Children under the age of 14 will not be permitted unless express written consent is given by dōTERRA. If consent is given, a separate ticket for the child will still need to be purchased. No children will be allowed at the Gala.


Convention Mondiale doTERRA 2019

Rejoignez-nous à la convention mondiale annuelle de doTERRA du 10 au 13 septembre 2019 à Salt Lake City pour apprendre et célébrer avec nous! Venez en apprendre davantage sur les huiles essentielles, être inspiré et découvrir comment vous pouvez changer les choses et avoir un impact positif sur la vie de votre entourage. Nous avons hâte de vous y voir!

Tout nouveau cette année! Le gala de reconnaissance aura lieu mardi soir et les sessions générales auront lieu mercredi, jeudi et vendredi. Cependant, nous ouvrirons les inscriptions tôt lundi soir et une présentation "clé du succès" clôturera la semaine le samedi matin.

Transferts de billets et annulation


Transfert de billet : Gratuit (1er Avril – 20 Août 2019). Un billet ne peut être transféré qu'une seule fois. Le paiement des transferts est entièrement arrangé par vous. Nous ne transférons pas le paiement au nouveau détenteur de billet.


Annulation du billet: Gratuit (1er Avril – 20 Août 2019).


Politique de transfert de billets
Gratuit: du 1er avril au 20 août. Un billet ne peut être transféré qu'une seule fois.
Pour traiter votre transfert de billet, envoyez un e-mail à convention@doterra.com ou appelez le service clientèle avec votre demande de transfert.
Le paiement des transferts est entièrement arrangé par les personnes impliquées. Nous ne transférons pas le paiement au nouveau détenteur de billet.
Nous ne pouvons transférer que la totalité de votre commande, ce qui signifie que votre ticket de session générale et tous les tickets d'activité supplémentaires achetés seront transférés. Cela comprend le gala, la formation "clé du succès", les visites de campus et le yoga.
Pour transférer des billets d'activité individuels, il vous suffit de les remettre à qui vous souhaitez les transférer sur place lors de l'événement. Le paiement est arrangé par les personnes impliquées.
Politique d'annulation
Gratuit: 1er avril au 20 août.
Envoyez un e-mail à convention@doterra.com ou appelez le service clientèle avec votre demande d'annulation.
Politique de changement de piste (A/B)
Le changement de pistes est possible en fonction de leurs disponibilités. Nous ne pouvons pas faire d'exception si les pistes sont déjà pleines. Envoyez un e-mail à convention@doterra.com ou appelez le service clientèle pour les demandes de changement de piste. Les changements de piste peuvent être faits jusqu'au 20 Août.
Questions sur l'inscription
Pour les questions concerncant la convention, veuillez envoyer un courriel à convention@doterra.com ou contactez le service clientèle au1-800-411-8151. 
Veuillez noter: 
*Vous devez acheter un pass complet pour la convention pour pouvoir acheter des billets d'activité (Gala, yoga, formation "clé du succès", etc.). Si vous n'achetez pas de pass de convention complet, vos tickets d'activité seront annulés / remboursés.
*Les enfants de moins de 14 ans ne seront pas autorisés à moins d'un consentement écrit exprès de doTERRA. Si le consentement est donné, un billet séparé pour l'enfant devra quand même être acheté. Aucun enfant ne sera admis au gala.

Envoyez un e-mail à convention@doterra.com ou appelez le service clientèle pour les demandes de changement de piste. Les changements de piste peuvent être faits jusqu'au 20 Août.

I mässbroschyren ges också information om seminarierna som 
kommer att presenteras och vilka som är seminarieföreläsare. 
Normalt hålls seminarier om olika populära länder i hela världen 
samt speciella seminarier om skattekonsekvenser vid köp av 
bostad utomlands, pensionering utomlands och 
hur man lyckas med en utlandsflytt.

description.text:
Newport Folk Festival
July 26, 27, 28, 2019
Since 1959, the Newport Folk Festival has held a unique place in America’s musical and cultural history as the granddaddy of all American music festivals. That influence continues today, serving the fans who crave innovation but appreciate tradition. Join us for this year's Festival in Newport Rhode Island held July 26-28, 2019.
see Newport Folk Festival web site 

PLEASE NOTE: Due to world events,  and to ensure our fans safety and efficiency of our entry operations, there will be no daily in-and-out or re-entry permitted.  Our top priority is to provide a safe experience for all fans', employees and artists. For your convenience the visitors center is inside the festival grounds, and fans' will have access to the bathrooms and ATM. We ask that you please pack accordingly to adjust to this policy. 
GENERAL INFORMATION


There is a 6 ticket limit per household, per festival day, on admission tickets. This includes children's tickets (ages 3-12).


Parking passes are not counted in the daily ticket limit.


For example, a household can purchase six 3-day tickets or up to six single day tickets for each day, plus parking, while supplies last.


Please adhere to published ticket limits. Persons who exceed limits may be unable to purchase or may have any or all their orders and tickets cancelled without notice. This includes orders associated with the same name, e-mail address, billing address, credit card number or other information.


There is a delivery delay on all mobile or print at home tickets until July 17, 2019.




All sales are final; no refunds or exchanges will be processed by Newport Folk.


All 2 and 3 day passes may not be split by day.


Newport Folk Festival is held rain or shine.


Artists are subject to change without notice.


Tickets are subject to service charges.


Once you purchase, you will receive an order confirmation email from Eventbrite on behalf of Newport Folk Festival.


If you do not see your order confirmation in your inbox, make sure to check your junk/spam folder.


If you have not received your order confirmation or are having any other technical issues with your order, click here to contact Eventbrite: https://www.eventbrite.com/support/contact-us


For general festival information, please visit http://www.newportfolk.org/info/



**** Only purchase Newport Folk Festival tickets from the official Newport Folk Festival ticketing page (you're here!). If you purchase from another source, you risk purchasing a counterfeit or invalid ticket. Newport Folk Festival cannot guarantee tickets purchased from unofficial sources like un-authorized 3rd party resellers (individuals or brokers).



PAY WITH AFFIRM: How does the payment plan work?
Affirm offers clear, simple financing to split your Eventbrite order into 3 or 6 monthly payments. Once you select Monthly Payments with Affirm on the Eventbrite checkout page, you will need to confirm your loan on Affirm. We highly recommend that you sign up for an Affirm account prior to the on sale to speed up the checkout process of your tickets. Make sure you pay your Affirm bills on or before your due dates.

How do I purchase a ticket using Affirm?
You will need to select a ticket, click order now, and then on the purchase page select Monthly Payment with Affirm from the payment method drop down. 
AFFIRM FAQ LINK:   https://www.affirm.com/faqs/
 To sign up for Affirm, you must:


Be 18 years or older (19 years or older in Alabama or if you’re a ward of the state in Nebraska).


Provide a valid U.S. or APO/FPO/DPO home address. Buy with Affirm is not currently available to West Virginia residents.


Provide a valid U.S. mobile or VoIP number and agree to receive SMS texts. The phone account must be registered in your name.


Provide your full name, email address, date of birth, and the last 4 digits of your social security number to help us verify your identity. 


There are two ways to sign up for Affirm:


Create an Affirm account at www.affirm.com/account in just a few easy steps
Select Affirm as your payment method while checking out with your tickets on Eventbrite.

name.text: 24th Annual Central Avenue Jazz Festival
name.html: 24th Annual Central Avenue Jazz Festival

description.text:
The 24th Annual Central Avenue Jazz Festival celebrates the legacy of the Historic Central Avenue and is one of the last few genuine jazz celebrations left in the Southern California region. This family-friendly festival allows the entire Los Angeles community to honor the history of Central Avenue by paying tribute to jazz greats such as Louis Armstrong, Billie Holiday, Charles Mingus and Dexter Gordon, while putting a spotlight on the younger emerging artists that are continuing this rich art form.
This year’s festivities will take place along Central Avenue, between Vernon Avenue and Martin Luther King Boulevard from 11am to 7pm, July 27th & 28th. 
We will feature live jazz performances on 3 stages, in addition to the historical Dunbar Hotel, a diverse selection of culinary experiences, as well as, Pavilions for Art, Business & Employment Resources, Health & Wellness and Youth.
For more information on the 24th Annual Central Avenue Jazz Festival, including forms for sponsors, vendors or volunteers, please visit  www.centralavejazzfest.com. Talent for this year’s jazz festival is scheduled to be announced in May.
